{"tid":2183161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵督導證8.31警阻救護入站","createTime":"2020-08-31T18:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T05:24:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b8fd1b2e45d55a00fd508f7ea6d3fd06b9072fb0","tid":2183161,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/B5QH2ZN3GNAWHOG4ZLLL5QMZRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FB5QH2ZN3GNAWHOG4ZLLL5QMZRA%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7gPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=7b00ee2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FB5QH2ZN3GNAWHOG4ZLLL5QMZRA%2F&h=32c1391b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/B5QH2ZN3GNAWHOG4ZLLL5QMZRA/</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8.31，警方衝入太子站無差別恐襲乘客後，隨即驅趕記者，站內發生甚麼事無人知曉。一直以諸多理由無公開當晚所有閉路電視片段的港鐵成為眾矢之的。「眾新聞」昨報道，引述一名事發時在場的港鐵督導員，承認當時港鐵與警方關係緊張，「完全摸唔透佢哋」，並確認有警員藉詞阻撓救護員入站急救傷者。"},{"pid":"840b9afd08f7033d4ecfda28e4538171932eb87f","tid":2183161,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdaeba488ce4f0a58cb75a4da7ec79f20b0bb87","tid":2183161,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"840b9afd08f7033d4ecfda28e4538171932eb87f","tid":2183161,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T18:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\